    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开办酒馆</h2><br>你是否向往过开办一家酒吧，出售自酿的手工啤酒？机会来了！祖父留给你的酒馆如今一片破败，让它重新焕发生机。随心所欲地装饰酒馆、打造独特的吧台氛围、探索属于你自己的配方、优化酿酒工艺流程、向顾客出售你的啤酒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/dbcfc54d0a26752e6194ff9b9df4c318.poster.avif?t=1753292905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/dbcfc54d0a26752e6194ff9b9df4c318.webm?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/dbcfc54d0a26752e6194ff9b9df4c318.mp4?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经营家族企业</h2><br>你的祖父在 60 年代白手起家，创立了一家小酒馆。他的手工啤酒很快在当地流行起来，生意蒸蒸日上。然后，大公司来了。这家小酒馆早已被人们遗忘，祖父也避世隐居多年。现在，该你大显身手，恢复这家酒馆昔日的荣光了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/2c69fc9a72d7730372f6803ab90cce75.poster.avif?t=1753292905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/2c69fc9a72d7730372f6803ab90cce75.webm?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/2c69fc9a72d7730372f6803ab90cce75.mp4?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握酿酒的艺术</h2><br>你继承了酿酒厂以及那些古老的设备。随着时间的推移（以及财务状况允许的情况下），你可以开始升级你的酿酒厂，逐渐掌握现代方法来酿造不同的手工啤酒。试验不同的酿酒原料，解锁全新配方以及更加先进的设备。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/97ce40d9b4ab44544dfd9f6a11a76946.poster.avif?t=1753292905\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/97ce40d9b4ab44544dfd9f6a11a76946.webm?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755180/extras/97ce40d9b4ab44544dfd9f6a11a76946.mp4?t=1753292905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为顾客的首选酒馆！</h2><br>精心设计，打造独一无二的酒馆。吸引新顾客的同时留住老顾客。不断改进你的啤酒，满足顾客的需求，赚取财富与名誉。掌握真实的酿酒机制、装满你的酒桶、不断发展你的生意！<br><br>你能扬名立万吗？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>酿造你梦寐以求的啤酒！探索全新配方、购买原料、解锁更加先进的设备<br></li><li>解锁全新家具与装饰，定制你的酒馆<br></li><li>立身扬名、吸引新顾客并保持老顾客的满意度<br></li><li>掌握手工酿制啤酒的每一步真实工艺流程<br></li><li>游玩多种小游戏，包括倒啤酒、换酒桶、搅拌原料、啤酒装瓶等<br></li><li>妥善打理生意、招贤纳士、保持酒馆库存充足<br></li><li>接受每日任务，获得更多金钱与经验奖励</li></ul>",
